      "description": "Hey there! Are you ready to drive home a total showstopper? I\u2019m parting ways with my absolute dream car, and let me tell you\u2014it is in incredible, like-new shape! It\u2019s been pampered since day one, kept tucked away in a garage, and looks just as stunning as the day it rolled off the lot. Not a scratch or a speck of dust to be found. It drives like a dream and is ready for its next big adventure. Come see it for yourself\u2014you won\u2019t be disappointed!",
