    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a pristine, collector-grade example of an analog performance icon. This vehicle features a high-revving, naturally aspirated powerplant with a perfectly calibrated VANOS system and individual throttle bodies for instantaneous throttle response. The drivetrain is anchored by a crisp-shifting Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory limited-slip differential, ensuring optimal power delivery. The chassis remains exceptionally tight, with zero subframe fatigue and all suspension kinematics maintained to factory tolerances. Finished in its original paint with a flawless undercarriage, this is a turn-key machine for the purist who demands mechanical perfection and uncompromising driving dynamics.",
